fridays meeting was gorbachevs first with high church 
officials since he became communist party chief in march 1985 such 
a meeting is unusual because party doctrine professes atheism 
the encounter reported by the official news agency tass was 
the lead item on the evening news program vremya and a front 
page story in todays editions of pravda and other soviet dailies 
tass said church head patriarch pimen had requested the meeting 
with the communist party chief to discuss the june celebration of 
