i mean who knows its a very unpredictable business 
i thought that if we could organize well and raise sufficient 
funds and really work at it as i always have there was a 
possibility that we could do it its never more than a possibility 
when you start 
dukakis sustained his theme for a year never mind the charisma 
here was a politician who had made government work 
