of it and that hed seen the future they wanted to achieve 
dukakis campaigned in iowa with the knowledge that he had a sure 
win a week later in new hampshire his neighboring state he 
campaigned in the south potentially hostile territory by leaving 
dixie to jackson and sen albert gore jr and concentrating on 
atypical southern voters jews and retirees in south florida 
hispanics in texas liberals throughout the region 
he was credited with a strong organization and was able to 
withstand the loss of his campaign manager and top aide john 
sasso in the flap over sassos role in campaign sabotage that 
revealed sen joseph bidens plagiarism and lapses of judgment 
he was also lucky that his third place showing in iowa wasnt 
viewed as the setback it might have been dukakis campaign chairman 
and longtime friend paul brountas said his iowa finish was 
perceived as a strong showing 
part of the plan was to do well enough in iowa so you could 
preserve the geographic advantage you have in new hampshire he 
said had he not done well in iowa his support in new hampshire 
may have softened 
critics and supporters will argue over whether dukakiss belated 
emergence was a triumph of money over message but it is 
indisputable that his financial success made much of it possible 
farmer who had been treasurer for john glenn in 1984 initially 
thought he could raise 65 million by the iowa caucuses in early 
february 
his figure was in line with what the wealthiest of the other 
democrats were able to raise but the dukakis campaign raised 17 
million by iowas caucus night a financial triumph that gave 
dukakis an enormous advantage over his rivals and paved the way for 
his emergence as the likely democratic presidential nominee 
his bankroll allowed him to run campaigns everywhere and to 
keep staff in place while opponents were collapsing their efforts 
into iowa and new hampshire 
he was prepared as a result when the campaign moved into the 
foreign territory of the south and he was able to survive 
consecutive losses in illinois and michigan he headed north after 
super tuesday with 2 million in the bank while his opponents were 
broke or in debt 
how was dukakis able to do it and not the others one reason was 
the network farmer built asking not just for contributions but for 
