importantly dukakiss own state had a booming economy and 
active democrats accustomed to giving 
the race for money in fact can be considered one of the major 
contests of 1988 and dukakis won it going away 
it isnt that candidates lose heart its that they run out of 
money farmer said money is the winnowing factor in this 
process 
