os strikebreaking ferries pride of bruges and pride of kent were 
steaming toward dover from the dutch port of rotterdam 
their crews were drawn from the 1100 p and o ferry workers who 
have returned to work on company terms the pickets are among 720 
refusing to go along with p and os plans to trim its staff and 
impose longer working hours p and o has fired the strikers 
