soviet leader mikhail gorbachev 
we think the comprehensive test ban is very important he 
added it is extremely important to stop the arms race 
the testing equipment was designed to feel the difference 
between nuclear and industrial explosions and very small 
earthquakes according to thomas cochran senior staff scientist 
for the defense council 
